Yvonne Nelson (mụrụ November 12, 1985)  bụ a Ghana omee, nlereanya, onye na-emeputa ihe nkiri na onye na-emeputa ihe
O meela n'ọtụtụ ihe nkiri, gụnyere House of Gold (2013), Any Other Monday, In April and Swings
A mụrụ Yvonne Nelson na Accra, Ghana
Ọ bụ agbụrụ nke ndị Fante na ndị Ga
Ọ malitere agụmakwụkwọ ya na St
Martin De Porres School na Accra  ma mesịa gaa Aggrey Memorial Senior High School
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na mahadum Zenith University College na Central University, ebe ọ gụrụ akara ugo mmụta na njikwa ọrụ mmadụ
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Ghana Institute of Management and Public Administration (GIMPA) na nzere Masters na International Relations na Diplomacy na 2020
Nelson, onye bụbu onye asọmpi Miss Ghana, gbagoro n'ihe nkiri nwere nnukwu ọrụ ihuenyo na Princess Tyra na Playboy
Ọ batara na mmepụta ihe nkiri na 2011
Ihe ngosi mbụ ya bụ ihe nkiri The Price, nke e wepụtara n'afọ ahụ
O mekwara Single na Married na 2012 na House of Gold na 2013
Nke ikpeazụ meriri foto kacha mma na Ghana Movie Awards na ihe nkiri Ghana kacha mma na 2013 City People Entertainment Awards
Na October 29, 2017, Nelson mụrụ nwa ya nwanyị Ryn Roberts na enyi ya nwoke mbụ, Jamie Roberts
Onye na-eme ihe nkiri gbachiri nkịtị banyere asịrị nke afọ ime ya ruo mgbe o kwupụtara ọmụmụ nwa ya nwanyị site na mkpuchi WOW Magazine
Nelson tọrọ ntọala Yvonne Nelson Glaucoma Foundation na 2010  iji nyere aka mepụta mmata gbasara ọrịa ahụ
Site na nkwado sitere n'aka ndị ama ama Ghana ndị ọzọ, o dekọtara otu ọrụ ebere na-eme ihe niile ma gbaa vidiyo iji nyere ndị mmadụ aka ịkụziri
Ọ gbakwara vidiyo iji nyere ndị mmadụ aka ịkụziri ndị mmadụ gbasara glaucoma
N'ihi ọrụ enyemaka ya karịsịa na glaucoma, GoWoman Magazine na Printex kwanyere ya ugwu maka ntọala ya na ọrụ ihe nkiri
N'oge na-adịbeghị anya, Nelson ewepụtala onwe ya, ya na ndị ọzọ a ma ama, itinyekwu olu na ọha mmadụ na ngagharị iwe megide nsogbu ike na mba ya
O duuru nche udo nke akpọrọ DumsorMustStop na Mee 16, 2015
A na-eji hashtag #dumsormussttop ugbu a na soshal midia iji kwalite nchegbu ndị Ghana gbasara nsogbu ike
Yvonne, onye a maara na ọ na-ekwu okwu n'oge na-adịbeghị anya banyere okwu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na mba ahụ kwara arịrị maka enweghị mmepe na Ghana kemgbe obodo ahụ nwetara nnwere onwe na 1957
Ọ gwara BBC na mkparịtaụka ya na o nwere ike chebara ịzọ ọkwa ọchịchị n'ọdịnihu
Onye na-eme ihe nkiri Yvonne Nelson dere na tweet na ọ na-atụ anya ụbọchị ndị Ghana ga-ajụ ịtụ vootu na ntuli aka onye isi ala iziga ndị ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị ozi
Enyere Yvonne Nelson ihe nrite pụrụ iche na "MTN Heroes of Change" iji kwado ọrụ ebere ya n'ịlụso glaucoma ọgụ
